ss=title> Re: Bloodbath...</span><hr size=1> Clarity is 7. Doesn't actually get to 7 until level 49 though.<br><br>In the beta, enchanters didn't have clarity. Bards had mana song. Breeze came out with Kunark.<br><br>Um.. I believe enchanters were originally meant to charm stuff to kill for them.. ugh it's been a long time.<br><br>And the exact wording was they would never put clarity on an item. That statement was also made under a different leadership. The newer, kinder, better verant is doing things that actually make the game better, rather then do things to keep the game conforming to their idiotic vision.<br><br>And I believe the first poster was saying the profile itself was fake, as in the person didn't have that stuff, rather then the bloodbath was fake. There is no way to put a fake item ON magelo. It reads packets as you zone. So, unless you can figure out a way to disguise another transfer as the packets you receive while zoning.. you couldn't get magelo to think you ahve something you don't. The effort involved in it would be enormous anyway, fo rsomething so easily verifiable. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uqalarrubican.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Qalar Rubican</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/7/02 1:01:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10614.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bloodbath...</span><hr size=1> Yeah I agree, Ring Events and Keyed Dungeons are WAY BETTER! <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showPrevMessage?topicID=10614.topic"> << Prev Topi